OL,3,CFather and son deaths in Ballygawley
OL,4,C'not suspicious'
OL,6,FThe sudden deaths of two men in Co
OL,7,FTyrone are not being treated as
OL,8,Fsuspicious, police have confirmed.
OL,10,FThe Garvaghy Road between Omagh and
OL,11,FBallygawley had been closed on Tuesday
OL,12,Fnight following the report of the two
OL,13,Fdeaths.
OL,15,FUTV understands the men were father
OL,16,Fand son.
OL,18,FThe PSNI confirmed that post-mortem
OL,19,Fexaminations have been completed.
OL,21,FAll road closures have now been lifted.
